{
  "stem": "17426.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 115.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a sense, unofficially, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everyone knew who I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the guards knew, the commandant knew me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sort of had a kind of a consideration for me and sort of, maybe, even a bit of respect.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In time, I was allowed to go to other camps by bicycle, with the car, with Tadek, to treat inmates in need of a dentist.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I found my brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were going to this particular camp that was just open, not far from us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we passed on the road, I noticed a bit of clothing, a sweater on one of the inmates that I sort of spotted that some-- that I remember.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And looking closer, I could see from his body build and his physiognomy that it is my brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to the guard, this is my brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said-- and, and some of the inmates were also from Dobra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they started to look at me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I pointed the finger not to say anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they also had guards, and I was afraid that those guards may arrest me and arrest even the guard that came with me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because this was not allowed officially.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just that the commandant was tolerant, and he said, OK, go out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you know, this is not allowed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If somebody catch me-- catch you, I don't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I passed by, and then I couldn't because Joe raised his eyes, and he saw me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I called my brother Joe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I knew that he's recognized me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I stopped with Tadek, and I said, Tadek, I want to go over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want to see him, I want to say hello.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
